        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_DataExport_ManualBillingCreditTransfer",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to export data related to manual billing credit transfers. It logs the usage of the report and retrieves detailed billing information for accounts with non-zero credit transfers. The procedure is part of a reporting schema and interacts with several tables to gather comprehensive billing data, which is then returned in a structured format."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
